      "parameters": {
        "content": "## VAPT Bot C — Pentester Group Dispatcher\n\n**Bot:** Telegram Bot C — Pentester Group\n**Validasi:** Hanya menerima pesan dari `PENTESTER_GROUP_CHAT_ID`\n\n**Routing:**\n- `/summary` → C1 (Shared Summary Generator)\n- `/update_activity` (init) → C3 Init Activity\n- `/update_activity` (session aktif) → C3 Session Handler\n- `/add_vuln` (init) → C4 Init Vuln\n- `/add_vuln` (session aktif) → C4 Session Handler\n- `/help`, `/start` → pesan bantuan\n\n**Session:** Redis `vapt:session:{userId}` per user (TTL 1 jam)\n**Setup:** Set `PENTESTER_GROUP_CHAT_ID` dan `WF_ID_*` di n8n Variables",
